title: Promote dual-check drift warnings to test failures
---
In tools_builtin.ml, the dual path/shell safety checks log drift warnings when Coq and OCaml disagree. Ensure test runs surface drift as failures, not just log lines. Options: hook into Logs reporter, add a drift counter, or assert no drift in test teardown. Acceptance: drift between Coq and OCaml checks during tests causes test failure.